HEADWORD: Neocosmic
<hw>Ne`o*cos"mic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Neo-</ets>
+ <ets>cosmic</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to the universe in its
present state; specifically, pertaining to the races of men known to
history.</def>⟦br⟧
